Chart A

data(instacart)

instacart_weekends= filter(instacart, order_dow== 5:7, preserve= TRUE)

instacart_weekends %>%
  count(department) %>%
  mutate(department = fct_reorder(department, n)) %>% 
  plot_ly(x = ~department, y = ~n, color = ~ department, type = "bar", colors = "viridis")
